{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"Well, I learned a lot of things about ballooning,"},{"time":4000,"text":"especially at the end of these balloon flights"},{"time":8000,"text":"around the world I did with Brian Jones."},{"time":10000,"text":"When I took this picture,"},{"time":12000,"text":"the window was frozen because of the moisture of the night."},{"time":16000,"text":"And on the other side there was a rising sun."},{"time":18000,"text":"So, you see that on the other side of ice"},{"time":22000,"text":"you have the unknown,"},{"time":24000,"text":"you have the non-obvious,"},{"time":27000,"text":"you have the non-seen,"},{"time":29000,"text":"for the people who don't dare"},{"time":31000,"text":"to go through the ice."}]},{"cues":[{"time":33000,"text":"There are so many people"},{"time":35000,"text":"who prefer to suffer in the ice they know"},{"time":38000,"text":"instead of taking the risk of going through the ice"},{"time":41000,"text":"to see what there is on the other side."},{"time":44000,"text":"And I think that's one of the main problems of our society."},{"time":48000,"text":"We learn, maybe not the famous TED audience,"},{"time":51000,"text":"but so many other people learn,"},{"time":54000,"text":"that the unknown, the doubts,"},{"time":56000,"text":"the question marks are dangerous."},{"time":58000,"text":"And we have to resist to the changes."},{"time":61000,"text":"We have to keep everything under control."},{"time":65000,"text":"Well, the unknown is part of life."}]},{"cues":[{"time":68000,"text":"And in that sense, ballooning is a beautiful metaphor."},{"time":72000,"text":"Because in the balloon, like in life,"},{"time":75000,"text":"we go very well in unforeseen directions."},{"time":78000,"text":"We want to go in a direction,"},{"time":80000,"text":"but the winds push us in another direction, like in life."},{"time":83000,"text":"And as long as we fight horizontally,"},{"time":86000,"text":"against life, against the winds,"},{"time":89000,"text":"against what's happening to us,"},{"time":91000,"text":"life is a nightmare."}]},{"cues":[{"time":94000,"text":"How do we steer a balloon?"},{"time":96000,"text":"By understanding that the atmosphere"},{"time":98000,"text":"is made out of several different layers of wind"},{"time":101000,"text":"which all have different direction."},{"time":104000,"text":"So, then, we understand that if we want to change our trajectory,"},{"time":107000,"text":"in life, or in the balloon,"},{"time":110000,"text":"we have to change altitude."},{"time":112000,"text":"Changing altitude, in life,"},{"time":114000,"text":"that means raising to another psychological, philosophical,"},{"time":118000,"text":"spiritual level."},{"time":120000,"text":"But how do we do that?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":122000,"text":"In ballooning, or in life,"},{"time":124000,"text":"how do we change altitude?"},{"time":126000,"text":"How do we go from the metaphor"},{"time":128000,"text":"to something more practical that we can really"},{"time":130000,"text":"use every day?"},{"time":132000,"text":"Well, in a balloon it's easy, we have ballast."},{"time":134000,"text":"And when we drop the ballast overboard we climb."},{"time":139000,"text":"Sand, water, all the equipment we don't need anymore."},{"time":143000,"text":"And I think in life it should be exactly like this."}]},{"cues":[{"time":146000,"text":"You know, when people speak about pioneering spirit,"},{"time":149000,"text":"very often they believe that pioneers"},{"time":151000,"text":"are the ones who have new ideas."},{"time":153000,"text":"It's not true."},{"time":155000,"text":"The pioneers are not the ones who have new ideas,"},{"time":157000,"text":"because new ideas are so easy to have."},{"time":159000,"text":"We just close our eyes for a minute we all come back"},{"time":161000,"text":"with a lot of new ideas."},{"time":163000,"text":"No, the pioneer is the one who"},{"time":165000,"text":"allows himself to throw overboard a lot of ballast."},{"time":168000,"text":"Habits, certainties,"},{"time":171000,"text":"convictions, exclamation marks,"},{"time":176000,"text":"paradigms, dogmas."},{"time":178000,"text":"And when we are able to do that,"},{"time":180000,"text":"what happens?"},{"time":182000,"text":"Life is not anymore"},{"time":184000,"text":"just one line going in one direction"},{"time":188000,"text":"in one dimension. No."},{"time":190000,"text":"Life is going to be made out of all the possible lines"},{"time":194000,"text":"that go in all the possible directions"},{"time":196000,"text":"in three dimensions."}]},{"cues":[{"time":200000,"text":"And pioneering spirit will be each time we allow ourselves"},{"time":202000,"text":"to explore this vertical axis."},{"time":205000,"text":"Of course not just like the atmosphere in the balloon,"},{"time":207000,"text":"but in life itself."},{"time":209000,"text":"Explore this vertical axis, that means"},{"time":212000,"text":"explore all the different ways to do,"},{"time":214000,"text":"all the different ways to behave, all the different ways to think,"},{"time":218000,"text":"before we find the one that goes in the direction we wish."},{"time":223000,"text":"This is very practical."},{"time":225000,"text":"This can be in politics."},{"time":227000,"text":"This can be in spirituality."},{"time":229000,"text":"This can be in environment,"},{"time":231000,"text":"in finance, in education of children."}]},{"cues":[{"time":234000,"text":"I deeply believe"},{"time":236000,"text":"that life is a much greater adventure"},{"time":239000,"text":"if we manage to do politics"},{"time":241000,"text":"without the trench between the left and the right wing."},{"time":245000,"text":"Because we will throw away these political dogmas."},{"time":249000,"text":"I deeply believe that we can make much more protection of the environment"},{"time":253000,"text":"if we get rid -- if we throw overboard"},{"time":256000,"text":"this fundamentalism that some of the greens have showed in the past."},{"time":260000,"text":"And that we can aim for much higher spirituality"},{"time":263000,"text":"if we get rid of the religious dogmas."},{"time":265000,"text":"Throwing overboard, as ballast, to change our direction."}]},{"cues":[{"time":269000,"text":"Well, these basically are things I believed in such a long time."},{"time":272000,"text":"But actually I had to go around the world in a balloon"},{"time":274000,"text":"to be invited to talk about it."},{"time":276000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":279000,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":285000,"text":"It's clear that it's not easy to know which ballast to drop"},{"time":289000,"text":"and which altitude to take. Sometime we need"},{"time":291000,"text":"friends, family members or a psychiatrist."},{"time":294000,"text":"Well, in balloons we need weather men,"},{"time":297000,"text":"the one who calculate the direction of each layer of wind,"},{"time":301000,"text":"at which altitude, in order to help the balloonist."},{"time":304000,"text":"But sometimes it's very paradoxical."}]},{"cues":[{"time":307000,"text":"When Brian Jones and I were flying around the world,"},{"time":310000,"text":"the weather man asked us, one day, to fly"},{"time":312000,"text":"quite low, and very slow."},{"time":315000,"text":"And when we calculated we thought we're never going to make it"},{"time":317000,"text":"around the world at that speed."},{"time":320000,"text":"So, we disobeyed. We flew much higher, and double the speed."}]},{"cues":[{"time":324000,"text":"And I was so proud to have found that jetstream"},{"time":327000,"text":"that I called the weather man,"},{"time":329000,"text":"and I told him, \"Hey, guy, don't you think we're good pilots up there?"},{"time":332000,"text":"We fly twice the speed you predicted.\""},{"time":335000,"text":"And he told me, \"Don't do that. Go down immediately"},{"time":337000,"text":"in order to slow down.\""},{"time":339000,"text":"And I started to argue. I said, \"I'm not going to do that."},{"time":341000,"text":"We don't have enough gas to fly so slow.\""},{"time":344000,"text":"And he told me, \"Yes, but with the low pressure you have on your left"},{"time":347000,"text":"if you fly too fast, in a couple of hours"},{"time":350000,"text":"you will turn left and end up at the North Pole."},{"time":352000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":354000,"text":"And then he asked me --"},{"time":356000,"text":"and this is something I will never forget in my life --"},{"time":359000,"text":"he just asked me, \"You're the good pilot up there."},{"time":362000,"text":"What do you really want? You want to go very fast"},{"time":364000,"text":"in the wrong direction, or slowly in the good direction?"},{"time":367000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":370000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":372000,"text":"And this is why you need weathermen."},{"time":374000,"text":"This is why you need people with long-term vision."},{"time":377000,"text":"And this is precisely what fails"},{"time":380000,"text":"in the political visions we have now,"},{"time":383000,"text":"in the political governments."},{"time":385000,"text":"We are burning, as you heard,"},{"time":387000,"text":"so much energy,"},{"time":389000,"text":"not understanding that such an unsustainable"},{"time":393000,"text":"way of life cannot last for long."},{"time":396000,"text":"So, we went down actually."},{"time":399000,"text":"We slowed down. And we went through moments of fears"},{"time":403000,"text":"because we had no idea how the little amount of gas"},{"time":405000,"text":"we had in the balloon"},{"time":407000,"text":"could allow us to travel 45,000 kilometers."},{"time":411000,"text":"But we were expected to have doubts; we're expected to have fears."},{"time":414000,"text":"And actually this is where the adventure really started."}]},{"cues":[{"time":417000,"text":"When we were flying over the Sahara and India"},{"time":419000,"text":"it was nice holidays."},{"time":421000,"text":"We could land anytime and fly back home with an airplane."},{"time":424000,"text":"In the middle of the Pacific,"},{"time":426000,"text":"when you don't have the good winds, you cannot land,"},{"time":428000,"text":"you cannot go back."},{"time":430000,"text":"That's a crisis."},{"time":432000,"text":"That's the moment when you have to wake up"},{"time":434000,"text":"from the automatic way of thinking."},{"time":436000,"text":"That's the moment when you have to motivate"},{"time":438000,"text":"your inner potential,"},{"time":440000,"text":"your creativity."},{"time":442000,"text":"That's when you throw out all the ballast,"},{"time":444000,"text":"all the certainties,"},{"time":446000,"text":"in order to adapt to the new situation."}]},{"cues":[{"time":448000,"text":"And actually, we changed completely our flight plan."},{"time":451000,"text":"We changed completely our strategy."},{"time":453000,"text":"And after 20 days we landed successfully in Egypt."},{"time":456000,"text":"But if I show you this picture"},{"time":458000,"text":"it's not to tell you how happy we were."},{"time":461000,"text":"It's to show you how much gas was left"},{"time":463000,"text":"in the last bottles."},{"time":465000,"text":"We took off with 3.7 tons of liquid propane."},{"time":470000,"text":"We landed with 40 kilos."}]},{"cues":[{"time":474000,"text":"When I saw that, I made a promise to myself."},{"time":477000,"text":"I made a promise that the next time I would fly around the world,"},{"time":480000,"text":"it would be with no fuel,"},{"time":483000,"text":"independent from fossil energies,"},{"time":486000,"text":"in order to be safe,"},{"time":489000,"text":"not to be threatened by the fuel gauge."},{"time":491000,"text":"I had no idea how it was possible."},{"time":494000,"text":"I just thought it's a dream and I want to do it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":498000,"text":"And when the capsule of my balloon was introduced"},{"time":501000,"text":"officially in the Air and Space Museum in Washington,"},{"time":503000,"text":"together with the airplane of Charles Lindbergh,"},{"time":505000,"text":"with Apollo 11, with the Wright Brothers' Flyer,"},{"time":507000,"text":"with Chuck Yeager's 61,"},{"time":510000,"text":"I had really a thought then."},{"time":512000,"text":"I thought, well, the 20th century, that was brilliant."},{"time":514000,"text":"It allowed to do all those things there."},{"time":517000,"text":"But it will not be possible in the future any more."},{"time":520000,"text":"It takes too much energy. It will cost too much."},{"time":523000,"text":"It will be prohibited"},{"time":525000,"text":"because we'll have to save our natural resources"},{"time":527000,"text":"in a few decades from now."}]},{"cues":[{"time":529000,"text":"So how can we perpetuate"},{"time":531000,"text":"this pioneering spirit"},{"time":534000,"text":"with something that will be independent from fossil energy?"},{"time":538000,"text":"And this is when the project Solar Impulse"},{"time":540000,"text":"really started to"},{"time":543000,"text":"turn in my head."},{"time":545000,"text":"And I think it's a nice metaphor also"},{"time":547000,"text":"for the 21st century."},{"time":549000,"text":"Pioneering spirit should continue, but on another level."},{"time":553000,"text":"Not to conquer the planet or space,"},{"time":556000,"text":"not anymore, it has been done,"},{"time":558000,"text":"but rather to improve the quality of life."},{"time":561000,"text":"How can we go through the ice of certainty"},{"time":564000,"text":"in order to make the most incredible a possible thing?"},{"time":568000,"text":"What is today completely impossible --"},{"time":572000,"text":"get rid of our dependency on fossil energy."}]},{"cues":[{"time":575000,"text":"If you tell to people, we want to be independent"},{"time":577000,"text":"from fossil energy in our world,"},{"time":579000,"text":"people will laugh at you, except here,"},{"time":581000,"text":"where crazy people are invited to speak."},{"time":584000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":586000,"text":"So, the idea is that if we fly around the world"},{"time":590000,"text":"in a solar powered airplane,"},{"time":592000,"text":"using absolutely no fuel,"},{"time":594000,"text":"nobody ever could say in the future"},{"time":597000,"text":"that it's impossible to do it"},{"time":599000,"text":"for cars, for heating systems,"},{"time":601000,"text":"for computers, and so on and so on."}]},{"cues":[{"time":604000,"text":"Well, solar power airplanes are not new."},{"time":607000,"text":"They have flown in the past, but without"},{"time":609000,"text":"saving capabilities, without batteries."},{"time":612000,"text":"Which means that they have more proven"},{"time":614000,"text":"the limits of renewable energies"},{"time":616000,"text":"than the potential of it."},{"time":618000,"text":"If we want to show the potential,"},{"time":620000,"text":"we have to fly day and night."},{"time":623000,"text":"That means to load the batteries during the flight,"},{"time":626000,"text":"in order to spend the night on the batteries,"},{"time":629000,"text":"and fly the next day again."},{"time":631000,"text":"It has been made, already, on remote controlled"},{"time":635000,"text":"little airplane models, without pilots."}]},{"cues":[{"time":638000,"text":"But it stays an anecdote"},{"time":640000,"text":"because the public couldn't identify to it."},{"time":643000,"text":"I think you need a pilot in the plane"},{"time":645000,"text":"that can talk to the universities,"},{"time":647000,"text":"that can talk to students,"},{"time":649000,"text":"talk to politicians during the flight,"},{"time":651000,"text":"and really make it a human adventure."},{"time":653000,"text":"For that, unfortunately,"},{"time":655000,"text":"four meters wingspan is not enough."},{"time":658000,"text":"You need 64 meter wingspan."},{"time":661000,"text":"64 meter wingspan to carry one pilot, the batteries,"},{"time":665000,"text":"flies slowly enough with the aerodynamic efficiency."},{"time":669000,"text":"Why that? Because fuel is not easy to replace."},{"time":673000,"text":"That's for sure."},{"time":675000,"text":"And with 200 square meters of solar power on our plane,"},{"time":680000,"text":"we can produce the same energy"},{"time":683000,"text":"than 200 little lightbulbs."},{"time":685000,"text":"That means a Christmas tree, a big Christmas tree."}]},{"cues":[{"time":689000,"text":"So the question is, how can you carry a pilot around the world"},{"time":693000,"text":"with an airplane that uses"},{"time":695000,"text":"the same amount of energy as a big Christmas tree?"},{"time":698000,"text":"People will tell you it's impossible,"},{"time":700000,"text":"and that's exactly why we try to do it."},{"time":703000,"text":"We launched the project with my colleague Andre Borschberg"},{"time":706000,"text":"six years ago."},{"time":708000,"text":"We have now 70 people in the team working on it."},{"time":711000,"text":"We have gone through the stages of simulation, design,"},{"time":715000,"text":"computing, preparing the construction"},{"time":718000,"text":"of the first prototype."},{"time":720000,"text":"That has been achieved after two years of work."},{"time":723000,"text":"Cockpit, propeller, engine."},{"time":725000,"text":"Just the fuselage here, it's so light."},{"time":727000,"text":"It's not designed by an artist, but it could be."},{"time":730000,"text":"50 kilos for the entire fuselage."},{"time":732000,"text":"Couple of kilos more for the wing spars."}]},{"cues":[{"time":736000,"text":"This is the complete structure of the airplane."},{"time":739000,"text":"And one month ago we have unveiled it."},{"time":742000,"text":"You cannot imagine how it is for a team"},{"time":744000,"text":"who has been working six years on it"},{"time":746000,"text":"to show that it's not only a dream and a vision,"},{"time":749000,"text":"it's a real airplane."},{"time":751000,"text":"A real airplane that we could finally present."}]},{"cues":[{"time":754000,"text":"And what's the goal now?"},{"time":756000,"text":"The goal is to take off,"},{"time":760000,"text":"end of this year for the first test,"},{"time":762000,"text":"but mainly next year, spring or summer,"},{"time":766000,"text":"take off, on our own power,"},{"time":768000,"text":"without additional help, without being towed,"},{"time":771000,"text":"climb to 9,000 meters altitude."},{"time":774000,"text":"The same time we load the batteries,"},{"time":776000,"text":"we run the engines, and when we get at the maximum height,"},{"time":781000,"text":"we arrive at the beginning of the night."},{"time":783000,"text":"And there, there will be just one goal, just one:"},{"time":788000,"text":"reach the next sunrise before the batteries are empty."},{"time":791000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":794000,"text":"And this is exactly the symbol of our world."},{"time":797000,"text":"If our airplane is too heavy,"},{"time":799000,"text":"if the pilot wastes energy,"},{"time":801000,"text":"we'll never make it through the night."},{"time":803000,"text":"And in our world, if we keep on spoiling,"},{"time":806000,"text":"wasting our energy resources,"},{"time":808000,"text":"if we keep on building things that consume so much energy"},{"time":811000,"text":"that most of the companies now go bankrupt,"},{"time":816000,"text":"it's clear that we'll never give the planet to the next generation"},{"time":818000,"text":"without a major problem."}]},{"cues":[{"time":820000,"text":"So, you see that this airplane is more a symbol."},{"time":823000,"text":"I don't think it will transport 200 people"},{"time":825000,"text":"in the next years."},{"time":827000,"text":"But when Lindbergh crossed the Atlantic,"},{"time":829000,"text":"the payload was also just sufficient"},{"time":831000,"text":"for one person and some fuel."},{"time":835000,"text":"And 20 years later there were 200 people"},{"time":837000,"text":"in every airplane crossing the Atlantic."}]},{"cues":[{"time":839000,"text":"So, we have to start,"},{"time":841000,"text":"and show the example."},{"time":843000,"text":"A little bit like on this picture here."},{"time":845000,"text":"This is a painting from Magritte,"},{"time":847000,"text":"in the museum in Holland that I love so much."},{"time":850000,"text":"It's a pipe, and it's written, \"This is not a pipe.\""},{"time":853000,"text":"This is not an airplane."},{"time":856000,"text":"This is a symbol of what we can achieve"},{"time":859000,"text":"when we believe in the impossible,"},{"time":861000,"text":"when we have a team,"},{"time":863000,"text":"when we have pioneering spirit,"},{"time":866000,"text":"and especially when we understand"},{"time":868000,"text":"that all the certainties we have"},{"time":870000,"text":"should be thrown overboard."}]},{"cues":[{"time":873000,"text":"What pleases me very much"},{"time":875000,"text":"is that in the beginning I thought that we would have to fly"},{"time":877000,"text":"around the world with no fuel"},{"time":880000,"text":"in order to have our message been understood."},{"time":883000,"text":"And more and more, we're invited around the world with Andre"},{"time":886000,"text":"to talk about that project, to talk about the symbol of it,"},{"time":889000,"text":"invited by politicians, invited in energy forums,"},{"time":892000,"text":"in order to show that it's not anymore"},{"time":895000,"text":"completely stupid"},{"time":897000,"text":"to think about getting rid of the dependency"},{"time":899000,"text":"on fossil energies."}]},{"cues":[{"time":901000,"text":"So, through speeches like this one today,"},{"time":904000,"text":"through interviews, through meetings,"},{"time":907000,"text":"our goal is to get as many people possible on the team."},{"time":912000,"text":"The success will not come"},{"time":914000,"text":"if we \"just,\" quote, unquote,"},{"time":916000,"text":"fly around the world in a solar-powered airplane."},{"time":918000,"text":"No, the success will come"},{"time":921000,"text":"if enough people are motivated"},{"time":923000,"text":"to do exactly the same in their daily life,"},{"time":926000,"text":"save energy, go to renewables."},{"time":929000,"text":"And this is possible. You know, with the technologies we have today,"},{"time":932000,"text":"we can save between 30 and 50 percent"},{"time":935000,"text":"of the energy of a country in Europe,"},{"time":939000,"text":"and we can solve half of the rest with renewables."},{"time":942000,"text":"It leaves 25 or 30 percent for"},{"time":945000,"text":"oil, gas, coal, nuclear, or whatever."},{"time":949000,"text":"This is acceptable."}]},{"cues":[{"time":951000,"text":"This is why all the people who believe"},{"time":955000,"text":"in this type of spirit"},{"time":957000,"text":"are welcome to be on that team."},{"time":959000,"text":"You can just go on SolarImpulse.com, subscribe"},{"time":962000,"text":"to just be informed of what we're doing."},{"time":964000,"text":"But much more, to get advices,"},{"time":966000,"text":"to give your comments, to spread the word"},{"time":968000,"text":"that if it's possible in the air,"},{"time":971000,"text":"of course it's possible in the ground."}]},{"cues":[{"time":974000,"text":"And each time we have some ice in the future,"},{"time":978000,"text":"we have to know that life will be great,"},{"time":981000,"text":"and the success will be brilliant"},{"time":984000,"text":"if we dare to overcome our fear of the ice,"},{"time":987000,"text":"to go through the obstacle,"},{"time":989000,"text":"to go through the problem, in order to see what there is on the other side."},{"time":993000,"text":"So, you see, this is what we're doing on our side."},{"time":997000,"text":"Everyone has his goal, has his dreams,"},{"time":1000000,"text":"has his visions."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1003000,"text":"The question I leave you with now"},{"time":1005000,"text":"is which is the ballast"},{"time":1007000,"text":"you would like to throw overboard?"},{"time":1011000,"text":"Which will be the altitude at which"},{"time":1013000,"text":"you would like to fly in your life,"},{"time":1016000,"text":"to get to the success that you wish to have,"},{"time":1019000,"text":"to get to the point that really belongs to you,"},{"time":1023000,"text":"with the potential you have,"},{"time":1025000,"text":"and the one you can really fulfill?"},{"time":1028000,"text":"Because the most renewable energy we have"},{"time":1031000,"text":"is our own potential, and our own passion."},{"time":1034000,"text":"So, let's go for it, and I wish you an excellent adventure"},{"time":1036000,"text":"in the wings of the future. Thank you."},{"time":1038000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}